---
title: Roast Lamb Rump & Feta Potatoes with Nutty Veggies & Caramelised Onion Sauce
description: A roast lamb rump dinner is getting a makeover with caramelised onion chutney sauce spooned over for a sweet and
sticky glaze. The potatoes are putting on a show with a sprinkle of creamy feta and don’t worry, the veggies aren’t
being left behind, not when they are accessorised with pine nuts.
